    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2020-01-15</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2020-07-07T14:52:17Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Ending China's Exit Ban for American Citizens Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill bars an official of China's government from obtaining a visa to enter the United States if the official was involved in prohibiting a U.S. citizen from leaving China in an attempt to achieve certain goals, such as convincing a relative of the U.S. citizen to submit to Chinese government custody for prosecution. Any existing visa belonging to such an official shall be revoked. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Ending China's Exit Ban for American Citizens Act of 2020</title>
